{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871370426,"sessionID":"ses_285d27a16ffe0wLYGNrj8mZFua","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2ea0320015F1bGzMHxyRDrB","messageID":"msg_d7a2e94250013I3oBi7DvuvgYp","sessionID":"ses_285d27a16ffe0wLYGNrj8mZFua","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_03c6e5088740448e8ed5029a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing Helm Chart templates and values configuration for the AgentCube project.\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-030\n10: - **Module**: `manifests`\n11: - **Language**: YAML\n12: - - **Size**: L\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## Background\n17: \n18: [TODO: Describe the context and motivation for this change]\n19: \n20: ---\n21: \n22: ## Requirements\n23: \n24: ### AR-030-001: [Requirement Title]\n25: \n26: The system SHALL [expected behavior].\n27: \n28: #### Scenario: AR-030-001-A — [Scenario Title]\n29: \n30: - **GIVEN** [precondition]\n31: - **WHEN** [trigger]\n32: - **THEN** [expected outcome]\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## Out of Scope\n37: \n38: - [List items not covered in this spec]\n39: \n40: ## Dependencies\n41: \n42: - [List related ARs or specifications]\n\n(End of file - total 42 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing Helm Chart templates and values configuration for the AgentCube project.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-030\n- **Module**: `manifests`\n- **Language**: YAML\n- - **Size**: L\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\n[TODO: De